### IntelliJ Platform Gradle Plugin (v2.x) ###
# Downloaded IDE binaries, runIde sandbox, runtime indexes and caches.
# Generated by org.jetbrains.intellij.platform; can be gigabytes — never commit.
.intellijPlatform/

